results.name: Let Cn(x) be the n-th cyclotomic polynomial; a(n) is the first prime Cn(x) after Cn(1).
example: a(11)=12207031 because C11(x) is composite for x=2,3,4 and C11(5)=12207031 is prime.
results.author: _Don Reble_, Jun 28 2003
